{"tid":2179494,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［玩撚完］消息指：12名偷渡人士保釋機會不大，扣押完成程序至少半年。","createTime":"2020-08-29T06:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T07:44:12.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"50de19b04b4b3ccda987fe6b7373de02ace75c57","tid":2179494,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T06:59:58.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】12名涉及反修例案件的香港人涉嫌偷渡，被內地海警截獲。消息指，他們正被扣押在深圳鹽田看守所。有內地律師說，一般由偵查、起訴至完成審判要至少半年，期間可以保釋的機會不大。<br />\n<br />\n12人是星期日早上在西貢布袋澳登上快艇，計劃潛逃台灣，最終被內地海警截獲。據了解，12人被扣押在深圳鹽田看守所，香港警方已獲內地當局通報。根據內地刑事程序，會分三個階段處理案件，包括偵查、檢察及審理。公安局截獲12人後，最長可以扣押37日，其間要報請檢察院決定是否逮捕。獲批准逮捕後，公安會有多兩個月調查，有需要可以延長多五個月。完成調查後，檢察院會在一個半月內決定是否起訴，其間可以再發還公安調查。正式上到法院，一般會在三個月內完成審理，但亦有權延期。<br />\n<br />\n有內地律師估計，最快半年才會完成整個刑事程序，相信被捕人獲准保釋的機會不大。內地刑事辯護律師莫少平：「大陸刑事案件的審理期限跨度非常大。如果用延期程序，用了幾次延期，要計算起來差異非常大。大陸是一但被抓，在案件未有審結前，絕大部份是處於羈押狀態。中國取保候審的條件彈性比較大，除非懷孕了、要臨產了不適合羈押，甚至包括有重病，這個可能是比較硬性的條件。」<br />\n<br />\n被扣留的12人都涉及一些反修例案件，其中「香港故事」成員李宇軒亦涉嫌違反港區國安法，保釋條件是不准離開香港有研究香港案件的內地律師說，他們在內地服刑完後，公安可以將他們移送回香港。趙元勤：「（公安）可以通知香港警方，香港警方可以說這個人犯了危害國家的犯罪，到刑期（完結）前、通知我們。他們到崗警或者有個移送的過程，直接到關口，把這個人交給崗警，由崗警處理。」他又說觸犯港區國安法的人，應該交由香港法院審理，除非是國安法內指明的特別情況，內地才會有管轄權。"},{"pid":"47c895a2fbe0e8f5005c10f9a7d9540a59152409","tid":2179494,"uid":117276,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"支那坐完<br />\n如果仲有命返到香港分分鐘又要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1591c0dd445aa65687148950c0631e3615bbe6be","tid":2179494,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47c895a2fbe0e8f5005c10f9a7d9540a59152409","tid":2179494,"uid":117276,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"支那坐完<br />\n如果仲有命返到香港分分鐘又要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"頂得順日日食發霉野先有資格返嚟香港受<br />\n<br />\n仲未計國安法條數會唔會喺大陸計埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6bdd83318a9801ab4c05fc684f8004f9041b63","tid":2179494,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"想知道我有咩可以做到"},{"pid":"00add86940148c703afd745c849c704d71e4177f","tid":2179494,"uid":134012,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f6bdd83318a9801ab4c05fc684f8004f9041b63","tid":2179494,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"想知道我有咩可以做到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"Twitter推上熱門"},{"pid":"f517bd2195ebdda597cb19c3b8109904c9548977","tid":2179494,"uid":260065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c3699c3e8b4c06a17db3a50f5c678443567125","tid":2179494,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:04:34.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fbd68977d1f4d684a3816e2907afa9cb03f95f","tid":2179494,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"一定會迫交出同伴名單<br />\n參考鄭文傑事件<br />\n<br />\n他還表示，看到過其他被中國當局拘留的香港人。這些可能會加劇當前香港示威抗議者的擔憂：在中國的統治下，香港的自由正在受到侵蝕。<br />\n<br />\n「他們說他們為國保部門工作，所以沒有人權可言，」鄭文傑對BBC說。「他們隨後開始折磨。」<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯他如何描述自己所遭到的折磨?<br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑把雙臂舉過頭頂，向我展示了他是如何通過和手銬相連的鎖鏈被吊起來的。<br />\n<br />\n他說，當局主要拷問他如何參與示威活動，目的是迫使他承認代表英國掀動香港動亂。<br />\n<br />\n「他們想知道英國在香港示威活動中扮演了什麼角色&mdash;&mdash;他們問我們向示威者提供了什麼支持、資金和裝備。」<br />\n<br />\n他說，他被迫連續幾個小時保持壓力姿勢，比如靠牆蹲下，如果移動就會挨打。<br />\n<br />\n「他們會打我的骨頭，比如腳踝&hellip;&hellip;或其他脆弱的部位。」<br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑稱，自己被迫使不能睡覺，審訊者強迫他唱中國國歌以保持清醒。<br />\n<br />\n他還相信，自己並非唯一遭到這種待遇的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n「我看到有一群香港人被逮捕和審訊。」<br />\n<br />\n「我聽到有人用廣東話說：『舉起手來&mdash;&mdash;你在示威中舉了旗，不是嗎?』」<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><br />\n<br />\n他說，在一堆1000多張香港抗議者的照片中，他被要求寫下任何認識的人的名字和他們之間的聯繫。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「國保明確表示，有一批又一批的香港抗議者被逮捕，並送到中國大陸拘捕。」<br />\n<br />\n他說，他被綁在椅子上，被抓住頭髮，審訊者嘗試用面部識別功能強迫他打開手機。<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><br />\n<br />\n他們成功解鎖後，把他向英國領事館發送的有關抗議活動信息的郵件打印出來。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「我告訴他們，我想百分百說清楚，英國沒有為抗議活動提供資源或幫助，」他對BBC說。<br />\n<br />\n但這毫無用處。最終，他們讓他錄下了兩段視頻供詞。他說一段是「背叛祖國」，另一段是「嫖娼」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-50484844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-50484844&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=645aebdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-50484844&h=2e118ef7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-50484844</a>"},{"pid":"246df10d634ed89cb9cb31ba03f90848317adfd8","tid":2179494,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00add86940148c703afd745c849c704d71e4177f","tid":2179494,"uid":134012,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f6bdd83318a9801ab4c05fc684f8004f9041b63","tid":2179494,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"想知道我有咩可以做到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"Twitter推上熱門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:05:34.000Z","msg":"其實我哋做嘅嘢好有限，人哋鬼佬照拉"},{"pid":"10297d82a8b83435a828032b1d124e22634de7a9","tid":2179494,"uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f6bdd83318a9801ab4c05fc684f8004f9041b63","tid":2179494,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"想知道我有咩可以做到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"其實冇<br />\n<br />\n香港人心底裏都係知道只能夠怪呢12個人唔好彩<br />\n<br />\n只不過邊個講出呢一句說話就係仆街<br />\n<br />\n但呢個係現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你睇呢件事喺社會上冇乜反應你就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a5d26366ed6c8b6e36926516b9e43673158491","tid":2179494,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"除非佢地肯好似李波咁<br />\n唔係都應該返唔到黎"},{"pid":"1b657c180d10d9532cc380b26c3c5b7e6da00bac","tid":2179494,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"隨時被認罪上cctv<br />\n又或者被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c8b029ebd6630f9e3166a0a8e41b0bb53b40c1","tid":2179494,"uid":336429,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"47c895a2fbe0e8f5005c10f9a7d9540a59152409","tid":2179494,"uid":117276,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"支那坐完<br />\n如果仲有命返到香港分分鐘又要坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"扣押程序半年,偷渡1年,返嚟再入暴動10年。<br />\n樂觀d都係坐11年半,最大嗰個到時40幾都仲可以喺黃圈做多20年先退休,最後生出嚟27仲可以去返讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以樂觀d啦,無事啦佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e492e481d9f60c0e05a76507976e35930d9b31","tid":2179494,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"